1
00:00:04,230 --> 00:00:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wasn't supposed to go like this.</i></font>

2
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry, Soji. 
This operation is a failure.</i></font>

3
00:00:12,980 --> 00:00:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's a woman worth?</font>

4
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beauty goes without saying.</font>

5
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it comes down to whether 
she's got lead at her core, don't you think?</font>

6
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I do.</font>

7
00:00:25,790 --> 00:00:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But doesn't the same go for men?</font>

8
00:00:28,840 --> 00:00:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and your word games.</font>

9
00:00:31,950 --> 00:00:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One thing worries me.</font>

10
00:00:34,130 --> 00:00:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As Niimi saw it, you can't afford 
to get so much as a scratch on you.</font>

11
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what if you're so scared,
you can't fight at your best?</font>

12
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that won't be a problem.</font>

13
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that's what I want to hear. 
A wound or two is a badge of honor.</font>

14
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I mean.</font>

15
00:00:53,850 --> 00:00:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll see this through 
without a scratch on us.</font>

16
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like you don't think much of me.</font>

17
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#ffffff">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

18
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ff7fc">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

19
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ef5fb">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

20
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ef2fb">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

21
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0eeefb">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

22
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ee8fa">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

23
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ee1f9">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

24
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ed9f8">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

25
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ecff7">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

26
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0ec5f6">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

27
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0db9f5">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

28
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0dacf4">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

29
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0d9ef2">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

30
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0d8ff1">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

31
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c7fef">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

32
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c6eed">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

33
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c5ceb">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

34
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c49ea">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

35
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What I can't understand is, why is he using
 two swords here? Is he desperate?</i></font>

36
00:02:55,110 --> 00:02:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, fine. I'll play his game.</i></font>

37
00:02:58,030 --> 00:03:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Two swords are good for defense,
as they keep the opponent at a distance.</i></font>

38
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what if...</i></font>

39
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I slip in close before you can stop me?</i></font>

40
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Exactly. You stop my strike 
with your long sword,</i></font>

41
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and try to finish me off 
with the short one.</i></font>

42
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I won't let that happen.</i></font>

43
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I even amaze myself.</i></font>

44
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your makeshift two-sword style
 bores me to tears!</font>

45
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we're even. Long swords only.</font>

46
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assuming no one butts in.</font>

47
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I guess I needn't worry.</font>

48
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't mind. 
Feel free to sit back and wait.</i></font>

49
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll take care of this.</i></font>

50
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry...</font>

51
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it'll take more than that.</font>

52
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what to expect.</font>

53
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now <i>that's</i> impressive.</font>

54
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll do anything to win.</font>

55
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not cowardice. Inspiration 
keeps coming to you in battle.</font>

56
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Truly a child of the sword,
battle made flesh.</font>

57
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But troubled times are coming.</font>

58
00:04:24,850 --> 00:04:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guns and cannons will carry the day.</font>

59
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yours is the last generation who can 
walk proud with swords at your side.</font>

60
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd been born later or earlier, 
your talent might never have blossomed.</font>

61
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okita!</font>

62
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:46,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, at least, ought to be grateful
 that you were born in this era.</font>

63
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But sadly, you have no ego.</font>

64
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're out here wielding 
your sword for other people.</font>

65
00:04:53,930 --> 00:04:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had a chance at the dream 
of all swordsmen:</font>

66
00:04:56,740 --> 00:05:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikazuchi, god of the blade.</font>

67
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same goes for you.</font>

68
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

69
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd sought only strength, 
you could have been a god of the sword.</font>

70
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Miburo couldn't have 
gotten on track without you.</font>

71
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You chose the group over yourself,</font>

72
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you've done a wonderful job
 setting the stage.</font>

73
00:05:19,850 --> 00:05:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you blathering about?</font>

74
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew I couldn't get to you if you knew 
where my strikes were coming from.</font>

75
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

76
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

77
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The short sword?</i></font>

78
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't tell me he planned it all.</i></font>

79
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He truly is Mikazuchi incarnate.</i></font>

80
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san, I have 
great respect for you.</font>

81
00:05:54,050 --> 00:05:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't stop. Keep walking.</font>

82
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't. M-My legs won't stop shaking.</font>

83
00:05:59,290 --> 00:06:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must walk.</font>

84
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't touch me, murderer.</font>

85
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't take orders from you.</font>

86
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen closely. You are free.</font>

87
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You needn't return to Shimabara.</font>

88
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave Kyoto.</font>

89
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then take me with you.</font>

90
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do that.</font>

91
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

92
00:06:25,850 --> 00:06:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm ready to die. I have no regrets.</font>

93
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cannot call suicide wrong.</font>

94
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend of mine died.</font>

95
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami, I want you to complete it.</font>

96
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your death leads to the future...</font>

97
00:06:57,280 --> 00:07:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is why you switched
 to two swords?</font>

98
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used my bad eye's blind spot
to attack with your dropped short sword?</font>

99
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare to die.</font>

100
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This fight is over. Don't draw it out.</font>

101
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

102
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not over yet!</font>

103
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't die yet. Not yet.</font>

104
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't where I die.</font>

105
00:07:36,370 --> 00:07:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata-san! Don't let him 
into the passage!</font>

106
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop him!</font>

107
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that.</i></font>

108
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So why?</i></font>

109
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why can't I move?</i></font>

110
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a man called Serizawa.</font>

111
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a true samurai, I guess.</font>

112
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's a "true" samurai?</font>

113
00:07:59,110 --> 00:08:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One who is born to a samurai family 
and who has a samurai soul.</font>

114
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A samurai with the soul of a samurai?</font>

115
00:08:05,910 --> 00:08:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't sound very unusual.</font>

116
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're wrong.</i></font>

117
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Samurai are fakes. 
There aren't any like that.</i></font>

118
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="44"><font color="#ffffff">Dojo</font></font></b></font></font>

119
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What domain do you serve? 
What's your school?</font>

120
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Challenging dojos.</font>

121
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And doing business.</font>

122
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12">{\an8}<font color="#3b3b3b">Ishida's
Medicinal
Powders</font></font></b></font></font>

123
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12">{\an8}<font color="#3b3b3b">Ishida's
Medicinal
Powders</font></font></b></font></font>

124
00:08:31,150 --> 00:08:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want something for 
those bruises and sprains?</font>

125
00:08:33,530 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I offer a discount on bulk purchases.</font>

126
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you buy some? 
I can see you're hurt.</font>

127
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you're a farmer's son.</font>

128
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got some nerve, 
making fools of us samurai.</font>

129
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ganging up for payback
with your faces hidden?</font>

130
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are any of you samurai?</font>

131
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you know we can 
cut you down for insolence?</font>

132
00:08:56,250 --> 00:08:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Get him!</font>

133
00:08:57,230 --> 00:09:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Peasants don't get 
to stand up to samurai.</font>

134
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Know your place now?</font>

135
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This doesn't hurt.
It doesn't even tickle.</i></font>

136
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're all a bunch of fakes.</i></font>

137
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who kept this country going 
in the age of peace?</i></font>

138
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who tilled its soil?</i></font>

139
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My mind was made up.</i></font>

140
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Samurai no longer 
had the souls of samurai.</i></font>

141
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If anyone did, they'd come 
from the peasantry.</i></font>

142
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My pet theory turned 
to certainty because of him.</i></font>

143
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm proud I was born a peasant.</i></font>

144
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="18"><font face="Georgia">2nd month, Bunkyu 2 (March, 1862)
Denzuin Temple, Edo</font></font></b></font>

145
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or I thought I was.</i></font>

146
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this where they're recruiting ronin?</font>

147
00:09:46,610 --> 00:09:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear they pay good money 
to cover travel arrangements.</font>

148
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you after a payout 
from the Shogunate, too?</font>

149
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't assume we're all the same.</font>

150
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to do something 
about the chaos in Kyoto.</font>

151
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? I like the look of you.</font>

152
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say no more.</font>

153
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll go together. For our country.</font>

154
00:10:11,090 --> 00:10:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's no inn, we sleep outside.</font>

155
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means we need to keep warm.</font>

156
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Traveling together, 
I realized what a ruffian he was.</i></font>

157
00:10:21,380 --> 00:10:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want the finest of women.</font>

158
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want a castle.</font>

159
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want my own country.</font>

160
00:10:28,450 --> 00:10:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In Kyoto, I got sick of his greed.</i></font>

161
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he led the Miburo with courage, 
strength, and occasionally, guile.</i></font>

162
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He had both daring and subtlety.</i></font>

163
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was always a danger,</i></font>

164
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he had charisma, too.</i></font>

165
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was everything I imagined 
a samurai to be. A true samurai.</i></font>

166
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can still fight.</font>

167
00:10:58,230 --> 00:10:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your worst, Hijikata.</font>

168
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Years of pent-up resentment
 and jealousy...</i></font>

169
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you don't have 
a more personal reason?</font>

170
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What right does a lowly peasant 
have to cut down a proud samurai?</i></font>

171
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata-san?</font>

172
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you live, 
I can't help feeling pathetic!</font>

173
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You grubby peasant!</font>

174
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that? There was no spirit in it.</font>

175
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll never get me to die that way.</font>

176
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one trusts a man who talks a good game
 but hesitates when it counts.</font>

177
00:11:42,730 --> 00:11:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata, I'm disappointed in you.</font>

178
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, you couldn't 
become a real demon.</font>

179
00:11:59,490 --> 00:12:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I going to die? 
Not here, that's for sure.</font>

180
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Damn it all.</font>

181
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough! I'll do it!</font>

182
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We made up our minds! 
We <i>have</i> to see it through!</font>

183
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Serizawa!</font>

184
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll end this. Right here.</font>

185
00:12:23,930 --> 00:12:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okita.</font>

186
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't fight like you did earlier
 in this narrow corridor.</font>

187
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do?</font>

188
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Tennen Rishin-school thrust? 
Yes. That would be your answer.</font>

189
00:12:42,050 --> 00:12:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that your famous "Triple Thrust"?</font>

190
00:12:44,610 --> 00:12:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard the grunts fussing about how
 "Okita-sensei does three thrusts in one."</font>

191
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never done it 
with a real sword before.</font>

192
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see it. I'll parry all three.</font>

193
00:12:59,010 --> 00:13:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll see about that.</font>

194
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To begin with...</i></font>

195
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here it comes!</font>

196
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...everyone miscounted.</i></font>

197
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One.</font>

198
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Two.</font>

199
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It seems like they didn't count 
the short thrust after the first one.</i></font>

200
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Three.</font>

201
00:13:18,530 --> 00:13:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it!</font>

202
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four?</font>

203
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See that?</font>

204
00:13:25,020 --> 00:13:28,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, everyone goes down
 on the fourth hit,</i></font>

205
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but in reality...</i></font>

206
00:13:31,770 --> 00:13:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there are five.</i></font>

207
00:13:37,370 --> 00:13:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He parried them all?</i></font>

208
00:13:39,470 --> 00:13:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was fun.</font>

209
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have any weaknesses?</font>

210
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I...</font>

211
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...don't!</font>

212
00:13:53,430 --> 00:13:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come here!</font>

213
00:13:56,090 --> 00:13:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>C-Crap.</i></font>

214
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm totally helpless.</i></font>

215
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Caught your leg on a writing desk? 
Luck sure turned its back on you.</font>

216
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over, Okita.</font>

217
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yu-bo!</font>

218
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A kid?</i></font>

219
00:14:20,410 --> 00:14:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsuguji.</font>

220
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsuguji, you're incurably wild,</font>

221
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there is one good thing about you.</font>

222
00:14:28,370 --> 00:14:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You care for those beneath you.</font>

223
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kind to children.</font>

224
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shove it, old geezer!</font>

225
00:14:35,770 --> 00:14:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#efefed">You want a piece of this?</font></font>

226
00:14:38,380 --> 00:14:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was my weakness.</i></font>

227
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a little thing, but it bothers me.</i></font>

228
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have the makings of 
a leader among samurai,</i></font>

229
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I can't ignore a chick 
that can't get back to its nest.</i></font>

230
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like that time...</i></font>

231
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look how dirty he is.</font>

232
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't he go somewhere else?</font>

233
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish he'd give it up.</font>

234
00:15:02,990 --> 00:15:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something came over me, 
and I ended up talking to him.</i></font>

235
00:15:08,490 --> 00:15:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why do I care about kids so much?</i></font>

236
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#fefefe">Because that's your true nature!</font></font>

237
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is not!</font>

238
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is not!</font>

239
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lintel?</font>

240
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beginner's mistake.</font>

241
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shit.</i></font>

242
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did I miscalculate?</i></font>

243
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Protecting the city of Kyoto 
is the ideal we Miburo strive for.</i></font>

244
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We needed to fight 
this battle to achieve it.</i></font>

245
00:15:58,350 --> 00:16:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Serizawa is too dangerous.
Too uncontrollable.</i></font>

246
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sooner or later, he'll cross a line
 we can't come back from.</i></font>

247
00:16:06,410 --> 00:16:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We need to protect 
the Miburo from fracturing.</i></font>

248
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And let's not forget the secret order 
from Aizu. That gives us an excuse.</i></font>

249
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the way of the sword to you?</font>

250
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a delusion.</font>

251
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sounded so sure when I told him 
this samurai stuff was all fake.</i></font>

252
00:16:27,430 --> 00:16:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now I'm faced with a real samurai.</i></font>

253
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I wrong?</i></font>

254
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I making a terrible mistake?</i></font>

255
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this man a true hero 
the Miburo can't do without?</i></font>

256
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he one of a kind? Is he the great man 
the nation needs in these desperate times?</i></font>

257
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And look at me, 
trying to kill him in a drunken sleep.</i></font>

258
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How could I not be disgusted with myself?</i></font>

259
00:16:54,190 --> 00:16:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

260
00:16:57,960 --> 00:17:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even I have things I can't give up.</i></font>

261
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let him die.</font>

262
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You came here for 
this stupid plan of mine</i></font>

263
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>without a doubt or a word of complaint.</i></font>

264
00:17:14,830 --> 00:17:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Soji.</i></font>

265
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We first met when you were nine.</i></font>

266
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I remember it like it was yesterday.</i></font>

267
00:17:25,050 --> 00:17:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're giving lessons?</font>

268
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure you can teach people 
without Kondo-san around?</font>

269
00:17:29,850 --> 00:17:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worry about yourself, stupid.</font>

270
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin sparring!</font>

271
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

272
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People were already 
calling you a prodigy.</i></font>

273
00:17:40,270 --> 00:17:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch my example.</font>

274
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how it's done.</font>

275
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew you'd make a name for yourself.</i></font>

276
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But you seemed bored somehow.</i></font>

277
00:17:57,690 --> 00:18:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fight? You're such a child.</font>

278
00:18:00,310 --> 00:18:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit following me.</font>

279
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm watching to make sure you don't run.</font>

280
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't have anyone who says they practice
 the Tennen Rishin school losing.</font>

281
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know what made you change,</i></font>

282
00:18:14,610 --> 00:18:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I felt I needed to support you.</i></font>

283
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't expect you to volunteer for 
that band of ronin first chance you got.</font>

284
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with helping folk
 now and then?</font>

285
00:18:28,670 --> 00:18:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going, too.</font>

286
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it. I won't protect you.</font>

287
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stick with you wherever you go.</font>

288
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you think you're keeping
 an eye on me.</font>

289
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the truth was,</i></font>

290
00:18:44,250 --> 00:18:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>you were always guarding me
 from behind.</i></font>

291
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You always believed in me 
and followed my lead.</i></font>

292
00:18:53,370 --> 00:18:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Look at you now, covered in blood.</i></font>

293
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're getting your own hands dirty.</i></font>

294
00:18:59,650 --> 00:19:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know I'll make more mistakes 
and regret every single one.</i></font>

295
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This still has to be 
the biggest mistake of my life.</i></font>

296
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But even so...</i></font>

297
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't let Soji die!</i></font>

298
00:19:25,940 --> 00:19:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll admit it. You're a genuine samurai.</i></font>

299
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The child of this era.
The man it needed.</i></font>

300
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata.</font>

301
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My name isn't worth preserving.</i></font>

302
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa Kamo, first commander 
of the Mibu Roshigumi,</font>

303
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure generations to come
 know your name.</font>

304
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm no one important, 
but he... he's a real treasure.</i></font>

305
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So die!</font>

306
00:19:57,920 --> 00:20:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you can strike without hesitation 
when it's for a comrade?</font>

307
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not for a cause or an organization, 
but for a petty, personal reason.</font>

308
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hijikata, what a small man you are.</i></font>

309
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You ought to get rid of that weakness.</i></font>

310
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You need to close your eyes to 
the little things to do something great.</i></font>

311
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You don't have Okita's beauty,
 nor his edge.</i></font>

312
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was a clumsy, brute-force strike.</i></font>

313
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

314
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But somehow...</i></font>

315
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your strike hurt 
more than all the others.</font>

316
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Die.</i></font>

317
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please die.</i></font>

318
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Die. Die.</i></font>

319
00:20:44,970 --> 00:20:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Die.</i></font>

320
00:20:44,970 --> 00:20:47,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-So you <i>do</i> have it in you.</font>

321
00:20:47,690 --> 00:20:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it. That's the way, Hijikata.</font>

322
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only...</font>

323
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to make sure.</font>

324
00:20:58,070 --> 00:20:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Damn it.</font>

325
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Serizawa!</font>

326
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Circle around back!</font>

327
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

328
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The inner room?</font>

329
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wasn't here.</font>

330
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can't be. Where did he go?</font>

331
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me he ran outside.</font>

332
00:21:25,230 --> 00:21:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad, Hijikata-san.</font>

333
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In his condition? Impossible.</i></font>

334
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did someone help him escape?</i></font>

335
00:21:43,410 --> 00:21:44,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

336
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">A Clumsy
 Strike</font></b></font></font>

337
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TImes New Roman"><font size="26"><b>{\an8}Next time</b></font></font></font>

338
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Hijikata Toshizo.</font>

339
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san, remember 
that drinking contest we had?</font>

340
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the story about the tortoise.</font>

341
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you'd keep fighting 
wherever you'd gotten to.</font>

342
00:23:35,090 --> 00:23:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd keep shouting, "Here I am!"</font>

343
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was what made a real man.</font>

344
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like I can still hear you 
saying all those things now.</font>

345
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: "Serizawa Kamo."</font>

346
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">Serizawa Kamo</font></b></font></font>

